title: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
headline: You’ve Unlocked a New Gift
subtitle: Blue & Green Camo Mammoth Avenger Livery
content:
Your gift of the Blue & Green Camo Mammoth Avenger livery for completing all 6 Project Overthrow missions will be available before July 21.

Stay tuned to the Rockstar Newswire for more limited-time events coming soon.
